Package: nmatransport
Type: Package
Title: Population Transportability and Transitivity Assessment in Network Meta-Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Mahmood", "Ahmad", email = "mahmood726@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: Extends standard network meta-analysis (NMA) to target populations
    by adjusting for differences in effect modifiers across the network.
    Implements matching-adjusted techniques for aggregate data NMA, automated
    transitivity assessments, and personalized treatment rankings to solve
    generalizability gaps in evidence synthesis.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/mahmood726-cyber/nmatransport
